coming after us.


186
0:7:56,69 --> 0:7:58,21
And we wouldn't have the money.


187
0:7:58,21 --> 0:8:1,64
And it would just mean he
wasn't working at a job


188
0:8:1,64 --> 0:8:3,76
where he might actually succeed.


189
0:8:3,76 --> 0:8:5,5
And the only thing he
really succeeded at


190
0:8:5,5 --> 0:8:6,84
was insurance sales.


191
0:8:6,84 --> 0:8:8,35
He could sell people anything.


192
0:8:8,35 --> 0:8:10,23
But he could never
hold onto the money,


193
0:8:10,23 --> 0:8:12,12
even to bring it home for food.


194
0:8:12,12 --> 0:8:15,92
Another one of his was-- this
was maybe the most mortifying.


195
0:8:15,92 --> 0:8:18,4
He invented-- we
didn't have dogs,


196
0:8:18,4 --> 0:8:20,73
