store or pet supply store.


199
0:8:26,88 --> 0:8:30,79
My father had an elevated dog
bed that sat on a metal frame


200
0:8:30,79 --> 0:8:33,2
and was sort of almost
like a hammock, strung


201
0:8:33,2 --> 0:8:34,39
kind of tightly.


202
0:8:34,39 --> 0:8:37,78
And I said, well,
why do dogs want


203
0:8:37,78 --> 0:8:39,773
to climb up on something
like that to sleep?


204
0:8:39,773 --> 0:8:41,814
If they want to climb up,
they'll sleep on a sofa


205
0:8:41,814 --> 0:8:43,49
or they'll sleep on the floor.


206
0:8:43,49 --> 0:8:46,16
And he said, no dogs
don't want to be


207
0:8:46,16 --> 0:8:48,25
down there where
the bugs might be.


208
0:8:48,25 --> 0:8:51,98
And I didn't no dogs
had a thing about bugs.


209
0:8:51,98 --> 0:8:56,25
And he said, also, this is the
only dog bed that's heated.


210
0:8:56,25 --> 0:8:59,79
And I thought,
well, dogs have fur.


211
0:8:59,79 --> 0:9:2,44
And I know some
small breeds, maybe,


212
0:9:2,44 --> 0:9:5,14
need to be warm, because
they don't have thick coats.


213
0:9:5,14 --> 0:9:7,85
But I said, well,
how are you going


214
0:9:7,85 --> 0:9:9,235
to get a dog to sleep on this?


215
0:9:9,235 --> 0:9:11,11
I don't think a dog's
going to sleep on this.


216
0:9:11,11 --> 0:9:14,95
And he said, we're making these,
and we're going to sell them.


217
0:9:14,95 --> 0:9:15,839
And they made them.


218
0:9:15,839 --> 0:9:17,63
They always made them
before they found out


219
0:9:17,63 --> 0:9:19,3
if there was a market.


220
0:9:19,3 --> 0:9:22,33
And he found out he couldn't
sell these everywhere


221
0:9:22,33 --> 0:9:24,9
where you would sell dog things.


222
0:9:24,9 --> 0:9:28,36
So then he knew a man who had a
