223
0:9:28,36 --> 0:9:32,16
So my father decided that
these would be a perfect object


224
0:9:32,16 --> 0:9:34,16
to sell out of a
service station.


225
0:9:34,16 --> 0:9:36,1
When you go to a service
station to get gas,


226
0:9:36,1 --> 0:9:37,51
and you see this
dog bed, and you've


227
0:9:37,51 --> 0:9:41,15
got dogs, well, of
